<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Jukboks Kiosk Setup</title>
<style>
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
html, body {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  overflow: hidden;
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f1e 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #16213e 100%);
  color: #fff;
}
.wrap {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 4vh 4vw;
}
.card {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 1100px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 6vw;
  align-items: center;
}
@media (max-aspect-ratio: 1/1) {
  .card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 4vh; }
}
.brand {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 18px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.logo {
  width: 64px; height: 64px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #a855f7);
  border-radius: 16px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 32px;
}
.brand h1 { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
.brand p { color: #a3a3c2; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 2px; }
h2 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.2; }
.steps { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.steps li {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 14px;
  padding: 12px 0;
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  color: #d4d4e7;
}
.num {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 32px; height: 32px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #a855f7);
  border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 15px;
}
.creds {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 16px 18px;
  margin-top: 8px;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #a3a3c2;
}
.creds strong { color: #fff; font-family: ui-monospace, Menlo, monospace; }
.qr-panel {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 24px;
  padding: 28px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
}
.qr-panel svg {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 360px;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
}
.qr-label {
  color: #1a1a2e;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-align: center;
}
.qr-hint {
  color: #6b7280;
  font-size: 13px;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 1.4;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="text-side">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="logo">&#9835;</div>
        <div>
          <h1>Jukboks</h1>
          <p>Kiosk awaiting setup</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2>Scan to set up this kiosk</h2>
      <ul class="steps">
        <li><div class="num">1</div><div>Scan the QR code with your phone &mdash; you&rsquo;ll join the setup Wi-Fi automatically.</div></li>
        <li><div class="num">2</div><div>The setup wizard opens on your phone (or visit <strong style="color:#fff">http://192.168.4.1</strong>).</div></li>
        <li><div class="num">3</div><div>Pick the venue&rsquo;s Wi-Fi, enter your venue code, and tap Complete.</div></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="creds">
        Manual join: network <strong>Jukboks-Setup</strong> &middot; password <strong>jukboks123</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="qr-side">
      <div class="qr-panel">
        {{QR_SVG}}
        <div class="qr-label">Scan to join setup Wi-Fi</div>
        <div class="qr-hint">iPhone &amp; Android both supported</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
